nodes.text: Conflict of Interest is a short story written by Laurie Burns that was originally published in Star Wars Adventure Journal 13 by West End Games in May 1997.
It was later published in Tales from the New Republic.
Set in 7 ABY, 3 years after Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, this was a 31-page story about a female undercover named Selby Jarrad.
